Jody Gilbert https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jody_Gilbert 0 Jody Gilbert (March 18, 1916 – February 3, 1979) was an American actress. She appeared in the films Chasing Danger, Everything Happens at Night, Little Old New York, Flowing Gold, Hudson's Bay, Never Give a Sucker an Even Break, Shadow of the Thin Man, Remember the Day, The Tuttles of Tahiti, The Affairs of Martha, Journey for Margaret, Strange Confession, Deadline for Murder, Decoy, Cross My Heart, Blondie's Holiday, Heading for Heaven, Albuquerque, Are You with It?, Shaggy, My Dear Secretary, Knock on Any Door, The Lost Tribe, The Lovable Cheat, Hellfire, One Last Fling, The Doctor and the Girl, The Blonde Bandit, Blonde Dynamite, House by the River, The Yellow Cab Man, Actor's and Sin and Willard, among others.
